@Abhayakara  I've added an alternative PR for this: https://github.com/dnssd-wg/draft-ietf-dnssd-tsr/pull/36

The idea as I recall was to have normative requirements for the 7 days in one place only, and refer to that place from other sections (incl Section 6) and not repeat the normative part necessarily.

That's ("MUST") currently in Section 2.
